	('/en/2013/03/05/turbo-badge-display-option-now-available-b67ea7ee90b4/','Mar 5, 2013. Turbo Badge Display Option Now Available. One of the most hotly requested features for Twitch Turbo has been, interestingly enough, the ability to toggle whether or not your Turbo badge is displayed in chat. Everyone seems to have their own reasons as to why they want to hide it, whether its to take the bulk off your username (If you‚Äôre Turbo, a channel mod, AND a channel subscriber, it adds up!) or not wanting to flaunt your expense, we understand the concerns and have delivered this feature. To toggle your Turbo Badge, head to Settings > Turbo > and use the check box labeled at the bottom of the page.',113,'Turbo Badge Display Option Now Available','

